The evidence with the title 'Easy money, impossible debt: how predatory lending traps ... ' says Feb 27, 2013  ... Borrowers frequently end up taking out multiple loans – with annual interest rates of 456% for payday loans and 300% for title loans – as they fall  ... Who work in payday or title loan stores are under heavy, constant pressure to lend money to people they know will soon be trapped in debt they cannot pay off. 
